Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: John Glenn and the presidency
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xcbz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Mar 1984
Astronaut Glenn comes down to earth after poor showing in first vote for Democrat presidential nominations. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less